source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05201_000030_RYNE<tab>It worked! Both wind and fire have answered the call!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05201_000030_RYNE<tab>に、ニ属性の同時神降ろし……成功です……！

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05201_000050_RYNE<tab>So many of them... But nothing we can't handle!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05201_000050_RYNE<tab>なんて数の罪喰い……迎撃をお願いします！

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05201_000060_RYNE<tab>I call...upon the power of Shiva!
TEXT_VOICEMAN_05201_000080_GAIA<tab>No! She's lost control! You've got to stop her!
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_05201_000080_GAIAどうみても暴走してるじゃない！
今すぐ倒してやらないと……！
